Creating Profit Margin YOY 11

Go to Charts and drag Combo chart to the sheet. Resize the object then change the title to ‘Profit Margin YOY’.

Click on Add Dimension and select Month then click on Add Measure to add Gross Profit Margin. Turn off the Master measure formatting select number formatting with a percentage and no decimal place

Click on Add under height of bars (It should be under Data and then Measures) and select YOY. Turn off the Master measure format then select number formatting with no decimal places.

Click on Appearance and then click on Presentation. Check the box next to Show Data Points.

Next click on color (also under Appearance). Turn off the legend

Click on Y-axis: Gross Profit Margin and select Narrow under scale
